ince_last_delinq` | 마지막 연체 이후 경과 월수 |\n","| `mths_since_last_record` | 마지막 공적 기록 이후 경과 월수 |\n","\n","---\n","\n","## 💡 추가 참고 사항\n","\n","* **제외된 변수:** `mths_since_issue_d` (최근 대출 발행일로부터 경과 월수)\n","* 본 가이드의 예시에는 포함되지 않았으나, 실제 분석 시 이 변수를 추가하면 **예측 성능(Prediction Scores)을 더욱 향상**시킬 수 있습니다."],"metadata":{"id":"wR8o6XRnncWh"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["## 2 General Preprocessing\n","a Discrete variables - Dummy columns"],"metadata":{"id":"_Wnt3sRxnhYQ"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["#creating dummy variables. adding new columns of values 1 or 0.\n","# ex for Gender=Male, we use 0 Non 1 True. etc\n","# single dummy variable is sufficient for two categories\n","# if there are 4 categories, we need only 3 categories in our prediction model\n","# we use the function\n","pd.get_dummies(loan_data['grade'], prefix = 'grade', prefix_sep = ':').head()"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":206},"id":"UfuPO6kXneZH","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1768891211690,"user_tz":-540,"elapsed":34,"user":{"displayName":"Young Mark","userId":"08915244444976601721"}},"outputId":"ae9e7877-70b5-49e0-8170-3485de1489b3"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":["   grade:A  grade:B  grade:C  grade:D  grade:E  grade:F  grade:G\n","0    False     True    False    False    False    False    False\n","1    False    False     True    False    False    False    False\n","2    False    False     True    False    False    False    False\n","3    False    False     True    False    False    False    False\n","4    False     True    False    False    False    False    False"],"text/html":["\n","  <div id=\"df-2fbeacd1-4ea1-4a67-b1a9-1534c1b0c699\" class=\"colab-df-container\">\n","    <div>\n","<style scoped>\n","    .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type {\n","        vertical-align: middle;\n","    }\n","\n","    .dataframe tbody tr th {\n","        vertical-align: top;\n","    }\n","\n","    .dataframe thead t